158092.name: Net ODA provided, total (% of GNI)
158092.description: Net Official development assistance (ODA) comprises grants or loans to developing countries and territories on the OECD/DAC list of aid recipients that are undertaken by the official sector with promotion of economic development and welfare as the main objective and at concessional financial terms. It is shown as a share of donors' GNI.

source.name: Data compiled from multiple sources by World Bank
source.dataPublisherSource: Geographical Distribution of Financial Flows to Developing Countries - OECD Development Assistance Committee, Development Co-operation Report - OECD Development Assistance Committee, International Development Statistics Database - OECD
